r />\n<br />\np.s 以目前指標睇 穿240機會不大 有機會係242-246左右造雙底<br />\n<br />\n原因  資金流不配合<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CVm4C9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCVm4C9W.jpg&h=47bbebd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b39fcd690b2b8e170b403175a942646a478203c","tid":965772,"uid":73586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"持倉<br />\n14051 0.159 50000（1/3注）<br />\n26748 0.229 10000"},{"pid":"2bf83a75b05d054c21b0d6cdac2e5d3109731322","tid":965772,"uid":138791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"Support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0a30c287fb439ab5c52ed7b26fc061e452beda","tid":965772,"uid":73586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T22:40:30.000Z","msg":"美股最後高收. 令港股今日有機會高開<br />\n維持高開加PUT 睇法~<br />\n加位253 - 254 <br />\n<br />\n升穿25400 不加第三注PUT .<br />\n暫不加中移PUT<br />\n<br />\n美股杜同NAS 小時多項指標都背馳.<br />\n日線MACD SAR 出Call signal <br />\n但接近20MA.<br />\n可能20MA 會有阻力."},{"pid":"6c6aa4494c04c7b6b8f7fd9d60931411ab38f7ee","tid":965772,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:31:49.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccaec3371db2112827925091edfc78ed99f7e0f","tid":965772,"uid":73586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"差五十點先到上加位<br />\n反而中左下加位 <br />\n加50000股輪"},{"pid":"55be4f01ed269f809e154524548cba238eafce9a","tid":965772,"uid":73586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"REVIEW 先~<br />\n<br />\n衝動往往好易奶野..<br />\n話說~<br />\n中移動隻put輪入既原因係因為係電話睇度跌穿左上升軌.<br />\n加上市況一般，先玩10000 股少少地玩下..<br />\n但係返去發覺原來未穿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n結果今日收市前走左<br />\n<br />\n0.229 &gt; 0.215 X 10000 = $ -140<br />\n<br />\nOn 9 事 之 2<br />\n策略上今日講過跌穿25000 開PUT<br />\n不過今日跌穿25000 係由高位25262 跌落黎..<br />\n跌Q左三百點先去開PUT..<br />\n變左止蝕位唔易訂<br />\n<br />\n最後今日收市前sell 50000 股 From 0.065 &gt;&gt; 0.058 -$350<br />\n<br />\nOn9 事 3<br />\n衝動又係好易奶野..<br />\n見到30 min 有背馳 + MACD + SAR 去開LONG CALL 256 <br />\n結果高位入&hellip; 淆就放左..<br />\n410 &gt;&gt; 382  = -280<br />\n<br />\nTotal 夾埋 輸左770 個大洋~<br />\n<br />\n特別mark 低睇下等自己知道錯乜&hellip;"},{"pid":"28eb7de712d76983782a2bc88c0f81bded6ba776","tid":965772,"uid":73586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"講返今日~ <br />\n大市先升後回, 最後跌65 點.<br />\n收針 呈待變形態, 係前底 13/11/2018 附近收到~ 都算唔錯~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖︰<br />\n一直呈降軌，20 天線及BB轉向下移，利淡<br />\n不過日線MTM 同ROC 背馳中.<br />\n主要可能成交唔夠既關係..<br />\n不過RSI 就跌到得37~<br />\n<br />\n值得留意頭肩頂仍然有效，資金流跌穿0 軸.<br />\n即使MTM ROC 都有背馳. 但都要等日線有足夠signal 才可以確認轉勢<br />\n暫日線以25313 21/12/2018 的低位作警戒位<br />\n<br />\n253 &ndash; 259 為密集區, <br />\n未穿20 MA 或 MACD 出call signal 前.<br />\n於253 &ndash; 259 以小時圖決定加PUT~<br />\n<br />\n小時圖︰<br />\n以小時圖睇, 資金流出配合跌勢, MTM 尾市收窄但ROC仍處於高負值<br />\n20 小時線 25326 於日線阻力相近<br />\n253 左右為有利開沽位置&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nMACD 收窄及 KDJ 低位出cross, <br />\n不過睇埋30 分鐘的ROC 及MTM 有嚴重背馳+曾經出針~<br />\nMACD + SAR 幾乎同步出signal<br />\n明日有機會反彈<br />\n(除非美股今晚大插500點以上)<br />\n<br />\n反彈先睇25300 <br />\n<br />\n利申︰ 14051  x 50000 股 (1/3) 倉<br />\n止賺︰未定<br />\n止蝕︰25450 &ndash; 25500"},{"pid":"ae1f6ef3475f6b217ac2ca5382482d9e68b8b926","tid":965772,"uid":18811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e62cdf9d525ae654fd25e3eeb3cdc8410c7066","tid":965772,"uid":73586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LZqviJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LZqviJ.jpg&h=2d230427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BA8ZzLp